  - m_Id: 5886803411165184
    m_Localized: Level Up!!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9823387960446976
    m_Localized: movement controls
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9824012173545472
    m_Localized: Use WASD keys to navigate your character through the battlefield.
      Move strategically to dodge enemy attacks and position yourself for combat.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9824539129122816
    m_Localized: "\u2022 RESPONSIVE 8-DIRECTIONAL MOVEMENT"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9824734000680960
    m_Localized: DASH ABILITY
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9824954407161856
    m_Localized: 'Double-tap any direction key to perform a rapid dash movement:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9825222251220992
    m_Localized: Dash Up
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9825418477539328
    m_Localized: Dash Down
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9825649730490368
    m_Localized: Dash Left
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9825802281521152
    m_Localized: Dash Right
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9826059023257600
    m_Localized: "\u2022 PERFECT FOR DODGING & REPOSITIONING"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9826387634393088
    m_Localized: Combat System
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9826655558144000
    m_Localized: AUTO ATTACK
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9826791537479680
    m_Localized: Your character automatically attacks nearby enemies. No need to
      click or press buttons - focus on positioning!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9827406837682176
    m_Localized: CONTINUOUS DAMAGE OUTPUT
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9827676669841408
    m_Localized: AUTO AIM
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9827808555536384
    m_Localized: Advanced targeting system automatically locks onto the nearest enemy.
      Your attacks always find their mark!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9827992798728192
    m_Localized: INTELLIGENT TARGET ACQUISITION
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9828514595311616
    m_Localized: PROGRESSION SYSTEM
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9828678802313216
    m_Localized: GAIN EXPERIENCE
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9828891487080448
    m_Localized: LEVEL UP - CHOOSE YOUR POWER
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9829117975302144
    m_Localized: Upon leveling up, select 1 of 3 random attributes to enhance. Build
      your character your way!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9829511023529984
    m_Localized: Attack
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9829714166255616
    m_Localized: Health
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9829939387797504
    m_Localized: Speed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9830479614152704
    m_Localized: Defeat enemies to earn XP. Fill the experience bar to level up and
      become stronger!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
